{"id": "cos046", "name": "Audio_Home_676_04_08", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Wake up.</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... Ugh...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Wake up, son.</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Five more minutes...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... Uhhh... Okay, I'm up...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Finally awake? You overslept for five minutes.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... I'm sorry...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Laziness corrupts the skills and weakens the mind. You are a member of the Neumann family. You are required to be in peak condition at all times... I will not allow you to bring shame upon our ancestors.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yes. I won't commit the same mistake again, father.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... Don't do it again. Go to the stables now. You have twenty-five minutes to prepare for your morning practice.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I'll go right away!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward 2 hours»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Father, mother, good morning.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "You must be hungry, right? Here's your breakfast.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yes, mother... Ah, thank you, Grace! It looks delicious!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "<i>*Chuckles*</i> I'm flattered. Enjoy your meal, young master.\nSir, Madam, do you want some more tea?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "I'm good. You can leave to take a break now.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "Understood. Thank you, sir.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... Your table manners are not refined enough.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "I, I'm sorry, father.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "It's not a big deal. It's not like we have any guests now.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "No good. One's everyday manners are a showcase of one's personality traits. Neglect is the beginning of all failures.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Yeah, yeah... Speaking of which, it's a holiday. You should sleep until you wake up naturally. It's not a big deal to skip just one morning practice...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Don't spoil him too much, Alyxia.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mother, I'm fine! Some physical activity in the morning gives me more energy as well!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Good boy. You really do work hard... Could it be, that you want to follow your father's footsteps and become a member of the exploration team?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yes!... <font size=\"1.6\">If I can...</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "The exploration team consists of well-rounded elites. Be it strength, knowledge, or intelligence, only the best of the best are allowed to join. With your performance right now, you won't even make it past the written test.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "If you truly want to be a member of the exploration team, you'll have to replace them, surpass yourself... You know very well what you should do, son.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yes! I will work even harder... to become someone as outstanding as father!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... Then prove it to me with your actions.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Understood! Mother, I'll be leaving first to study in my room!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Is that really enough for you? Should I ask Grace to make you some more?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "It's okay!\nI'm full!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "You... Sigh, why do you always have to be so strict?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "At his current level, he won't be able to join the exploration team. That's a fact. Sugarcoating the facts and giving him false consolation is not my style.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "But he is capable of doing it, right?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... Which is why I try my absolute best to provide him with the best in everything.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Just as I expected... But he's been working so hard, yet you don't even give him a single compliment. You just keep wanting him to be like you...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "You're wrong, Alyxia. I don't want him to be like me.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "Huh?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Colin Neumann Jr. The person who inherited my name will definitely not stop here... The Neumann family fell from glory in the past. It was me who brought this name back to the ranks of the elite, and I believe that my son can do even better than me. I am absolutely certain that he will surpass my achievements.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "He is my hope... I earnestly look forward to the arrival of that day.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... I will, father.</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">起きなさい。</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……うう…ん……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">早く起きなさい。</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "あと少しだけ……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……んん……分かったよ…起きるよ……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "やっと起きたのか？\n5分遅いぞ。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……ごめんなさい……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "懈怠は技術を鈍らせ、意思を崩す。\nNeumann家の一員としての誇りを持て。\n何時如何なる時も、最高の状態でなければならない……\nご先祖様に恥をかかせるな。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "はい。父上、二度と同じ過ちは繰り返しません。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……次はないぞ。\n早く馬小屋へ行きなさい。\n朝稽古まで残り25分だ。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "今すぐ向かいます！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»2時間早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "父上、母上、おはようございます。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "お腹がすいたでしょう？\nさあ、早く朝食になさい。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "はい、母上……あ、Graceさん！ありがとう。\nおいしそう！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "ふふ、いいんですよ。\n坊ちゃま、ごゆっくりお召し上がりください。\n旦那様、お茶のおかわりはいかがなさいますか？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "いや、結構だ。\nもう下がって、休みなさい。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "かしこまりました。\nでは、お言葉に甘えて。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……もう少し優雅に食べなさい。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ご、ごめんなさい、父上。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "いいじゃないですか。\nここは家の中なのだし。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "ダメだ。\n日頃の行いが、人格に現れる。\n甘えは堕落の始まりだ。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "はいはい、そうですね……\nそういえば、今日はお休みよね？\nもう少しゆっくり眠ればよかったのに。\n1日くらい朝稽古をお休みしても大丈夫でしょう？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "甘やかしすぎるな、Alyxia。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母上、僕は大丈夫です！\n朝から動いた方が、元気が出るので！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "いい子ね。\nとてもよく頑張っているわ……\nあなたも、お父様みたいに探査隊員になりたいのかしら？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "うん！……<font size=\"1.6\">もし、なれるなら……</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "探査隊に入るためには、身体能力だけでなく、知識や頭脳、全てにおいて優秀でなくてはならない。\nお前の能力では、筆記テストの時点で淘汰されるだろう。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "本当に探査隊員になりたいと望むのであれば、彼らに取って代わる必要がある。\n自らの殻を破る必要がある……何をすべきかは分かっているはずだ、息子よ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "分かっています！\n僕は……父上のような優秀な人になれるようより努力します！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……行動で示しなさい。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "はい！\n母上、僕は部屋に戻って勉強します！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "もうお腹はいっぱいなの？\nGraceに何か作ってもらわなくて大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "大丈夫です！\nお腹いっぱいです！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "あなた……はぁ……あの子に厳しすぎやしませんか？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "今のままでは探査隊に入れないのは事実だ。\n根拠のない慰めは私のやり方に反する。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "でも、あの子にはできるんでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……だから、私は私のできる限りのことをしているのだ。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "そういうことですか……\nでも、あの子はあんなに努力をしているのに、誉め言葉の一つも言ってやらないなんて……\nあの子もあなたのように……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "それは違う。\nAlyxia、私はあの子に私のようになってほしくはない。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Colin Neumann Jr.。\n私の名を継ぐ人間がこの程度で足を止めるはずがない……\nNeumannの名は一時は廃れたが、私がまた復活させた。\nそして、私の息子は私よりもよくやれると信じている。\nあいつは、必ず私を追い抜くだろう。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "あいつは、私の希望なのだ……\nいつかそんな日が来ればいいと望んでいる。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……必ず成し遂げます。父上。</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">醒醒。</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">快起來，兒子。</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "再睡一下……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……嗚……我起床就是了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "終於醒了？你晚了五分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……對不起……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "懈怠會腐化技巧，讓意志崩潰。你是 Neumann 家的一員，必須隨時處在巔峰狀態……可千萬別讓祖先蒙羞。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的。我不會再犯了，父親。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……下不為例。快去馬廄，你有二十五分鐘準備晨練。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我馬上去！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 2 小時»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "父親、母親，早安。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "一定餓了吧？快來吃早餐。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的，母親……啊，謝謝妳，Grace！看起來好好吃！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "呵呵，別客氣，少爺請慢用。\n老爺、夫人還要茶嗎？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不用了，下去休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "好的，謝謝老爺。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……吃相不夠優雅。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "對、對不起，父親。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "有什麼關係嘛，現在又沒外人在。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不行。日常禮儀會體現人格特質，輕忽就是墮落的開始。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "是、是……說起來明明是假日，應該睡飽了再起床嘛，晨練暫停一次也是可以的……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "別太寵他了，Alyxia。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母親，我沒問題的！早上活動一下，精神也比較好！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好孩子，這麼努力……難道你想和爸爸一樣，成為探勘隊的一員？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯！……<font size=\"1.6\">如果可以的話……</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "探勘隊需要全能的菁英，不管體能、知識與智慧，只有最優秀的人才能勝任。以你的表現，在筆試階段就會被 A.R.C. 排除。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "如果真想成為探勘隊的一員，就得取代他們，突破自己……你知道該怎麼做，兒子。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我知道！我會更加用心……變成像父親這樣優秀的人！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……用行動讓我看看吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的！母親，我先回房讀書了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "只吃這些夠嗎？要不要讓 Grace 多做一點？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "不用！我吃飽了！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "你啊……唉，總是那麼嚴格呢。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "以他目前的水準，無法加入探勘隊是事實。給他錯誤的安慰不是我的風格。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "但他能做到的吧？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……所以我才盡我所能給他最好的一切。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "果然是這樣……但他那麼努力，你卻一句稱讚也不給，只期望他和你一樣……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "錯了，Alyxia，我不要他變得像我。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Colin Neumann Jr.。繼承我名字的人，絕不會止步於此……Neumann 家曾經衰落過，是我讓這名字重回名門之列，而我相信兒子能做得比我更好，一定能超越我的成就。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "他是我的希望……我很期待那一天到來。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……我會的，父親。</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">일어나렴.</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......으음....음......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">아들, 어서 일어나렴.</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "조금만 더 잘게요.....\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......으음.....일어났어요......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "이제 일어났니? 5분 늦었구나.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": ".....죄송해요......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "게으름은 기술을 퇴화시키고 의지를 무너뜨린다. 넌 Neumann 가의 일원으로서 어느 때나 최고 자리에 서있을 수 있도록 해야 해... 우리 선조들의 얼굴에 먹칠을 해선 안된다.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "네. 다시는 그러지 않을 게요, 아버지.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......이번만 넘어가주마. 어서 마구간으로 가거라. 25분 동안 아침 훈련이다.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "지금 바로 가겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»2시간 앞으로 빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "아버지, 어머니, 일어나셨어요?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "배고프지? 어서 아침 먹으렴.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "네. 어머니... 아, Grace! 고맙습니다. 엄청 맛있을 것 같네요!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "호호, 아닙니다 도련님. 천천히 드세요.\n주인님, 사모님, 차 드시겠습니까?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "됐다. 가서 쉬도록 하거라.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "알겠습니다. 감사합니다, 주인님.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......먹을 땐 조금 더 우아하게 먹을 수 없겠니?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "죄, 죄송합니다, 아버지.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "무슨 상관이에요. \n지금은 집에 다른 사람도 와있지 않은데.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "안 돼. 일상에서의 행동은 그 사람의 인품을 나타낸다. 경솔함은 바로 몰락의 시작을 의미해.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "네~ 네... 그래도 휴일인데 잠도 푹 재워줘도 괜찮잖아요. 아침 훈련도 한 번쯤은...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "너무 그렇게 감싸주지 마, Alyxia.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "어머니, 괜찮습니다! 아침에 몸을 움직이면, 정신도 말짱해지는걸요!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "착한 아이로구나.\n이렇게 노력하는 걸 보니... 너도 아버지처럼 탐사대의 일원이 되고 싶은 거니?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "네! ......<font size=\"1.6\">만약 될 수만 있다면...</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "탐사대는 만능의 인재를 원하고 있다. 신체 능력뿐만 아니라 지식과 지혜 등 모든 면에서 뛰어난 인재만이 탐사대의 일원이 될 수 있어. 지금의 너로는 아마 A.R.C.의 필기 테스트에서도 떨어질 게 분명해.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "만약 진정으로 탐사대의 일원이 되고 싶다면, 그에 걸맞은 자격부터 갖춰야겠지. 자신의 한계를 넘어서라... 넌 이미 어떻게 해야 하는지 알고 있잖니, 아들.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "알고 있어요! 더 열심히 해서... 아버지같은 우수한 사람이 되도록 노력할게요!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......말이 아닌 행동으로 보여줬으면 좋겠구나.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "그렇게 할게요! 어머니, 먼저 공부하러 방으로 돌아가보겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "얼마 먹지도 않았잖니? Grace한테 더 만들어달라고 얘기할까?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "아니에요!\n배불러요!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "당신......하아... 그렇게까지 엄격하게 굴 필요 없잖아요?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "지금 저 수준으로는, 절대로 탐사대의 일을 수행할 수 없어. 위로와 격려는 내 교육 방침이 아니야.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "하지만 저 아이라면 충분히 해낼 수 있다고요!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......그래서 최대한 저 아이에게 가장 좋은 것들을 전수해주고 싶은 거야.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "그런 거였군요......하지만 저 아이, 저렇게나 노력하는데 당신은 칭찬 한마디 해주질 않잖아요. 저 아이가 얼마나 당신처럼 되기를 바라고 있는데...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "틀렸어, Alyxia. \n난 저 아이가 나처럼 되는 걸 바라지 않아.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "네?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Colin Neumann Jr.는 내 이름을 계승한 이름. 나 정도에서 멈추지 않을 거야.... 나는 몰락했던 Neumann 가를 내 이름을 걸고 다시 명가 반열에 오르도록 만들었어. 난 내 아들이 나보다 훨씬 더 잘 할 거라고 믿고 있어. 분명 나를 뛰어넘는 업적을 이루어낼 거라는 믿음.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "저 아이는 나의 희망이야...... 그날이 오기를 손꼽아 기다리고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......제가 꼭 해낼게요, 아버지.</font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">醒醒。</font>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">快起來，兒子。</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "再睡一下……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……嗚……我起床就是了……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "終於醒了？你晚了五分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……對不起……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "懈怠會腐化技巧，讓意志崩潰。你是 Neumann 家的一員，必須隨時處在巔峰狀態……可千萬別讓祖先蒙羞。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的。我不會再犯了，父親。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……下不為例。快去馬廄，你有二十五分鐘準備晨練。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我馬上去！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉 2 小時»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "父親、母親，早安。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "一定餓了吧？快來吃早餐。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的，母親……啊，謝謝妳，Grace！看起來好好吃！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "呵呵，別客氣，少爺請慢用。\n老爺、夫人還要茶嗎？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不用了，下去休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "好的，謝謝老爺。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……吃相不夠優雅。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "對、對不起，父親。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "有什麼關係嘛，現在又沒外人在。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不行。日常禮儀會體現人格特質，輕忽就是墮落的開始。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "是、是……說起來明明是假日，應該睡飽了再起床嘛，晨練暫停一次也是可以的……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "別太寵他了，Alyxia。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母親，我沒問題的！早上活動一下，精神也比較好！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好孩子，這麼努力……難道你想和爸爸一樣，成為探勘隊的一員？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯！……<font size=\"1.6\">如果可以的話……</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "探勘隊需要全能的菁英，不管體能、知識與智慧，只有最優秀的人才能勝任。以你的表現，在筆試階段就會被 A.R.C. 排除。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "如果真想成為探勘隊的一員，就得取代他們，突破自己……你知道該怎麼做，兒子。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我知道！我會更加用心……變成像父親這樣優秀的人！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……用行動讓我看看吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的！母親，我先回房讀書了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "只吃這些夠嗎？要不要讓 Grace 多做一點？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "不用！我吃飽了！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"],