溃。你是 Neumann 家的一员，必须随时处在巅峰状态……可千万别让祖先蒙羞。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的。我不会再犯了，父亲。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……下不为例。快去馬廄，你有二十五分钟准备晨练。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我马上去！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转 2 小时»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "父亲、母亲，早安。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "一定饿了吧？快来吃早餐。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的，母亲……啊，谢谢妳，Grace！看起来好好吃！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "呵呵，别客气，少爷请慢用。\n老爷、夫人还要茶吗？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不用了，下去休息吧。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Grace"], "content": "好的，谢谢老爷。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……吃相不够优雅。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "对、对不起，父亲。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "有什么关系嘛，现在又没外人在。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不行。日常礼仪会体现人格特质，轻忽就是堕落的开始。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "是、是……说起来明明是假日，应该睡饱了再起床嘛，晨练暂停一次也是可以的……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "别太宠他了，Alyxia。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "母亲，我没问题的！早上活动一下，精神也比较好！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "好孩子，这么努力……难道你想和爸爸一样，成为探勘队的一员？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "嗯！ ……<font size=\"1.6\">如果可以的话……</font>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "探勘队需要全能的菁英，不管体能、知识与智慧，只有最优秀的人才能胜任。以你的表现，在笔试阶段就会被 A.R.C. 排除。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "如果真想成为探勘队的一员，就得取代他们，突破自己……你知道该怎么做，儿子。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "我知道！我会更加用心……变成像父亲这样优秀的人！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……用行动让我看看吧。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "是的！母亲，我先回房读书了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "只吃这些够吗？要不要让 Grace 多做一点？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "不用！我吃饱了！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "你啊……唉，总是那么严格呢。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "以他目前的水准，无法加入探勘队是事实。给他错误的安慰不是我的风格。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "但他能做到的吧？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……所以我才尽我所能给他最好的一切。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "果然是这样……但他那么努力，你却一句称赞也不给，只期望他和你一样……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "错了，Alyxia，我不要他变得像我。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alyxia"], "content": "啊？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Colin Neumann Jr.。继承我名字的人，绝不会止步于此……Neumann 家曾经衰落过，是我让这名字重回名门之列，而我相信儿子能做得比我更好，一定能超越我的成就。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "他是我的希望……我很期待那一天到来。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……我会的，父亲。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}